      • expirationTimeSuggestion

        protected final org.apache.commons.lang.mutable.MutableLong expirationTimeSuggestion
        The possible time this Session may be inactive and available for expiration. This value is an optimization for Terracotta clustered environments, to avoid faulting object in, unless we have a best guess that it may be out of date. We also choose not to use the m_accessed field directly, to avoid updating the SHARED (on every box) data structure, except every inactive/2 period.

      • m_inactiveInterval

        protected int m_inactiveInterval
        Seconds of inactive time before being automatically invalidated - 0 turns off this feature.
